1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,000
 Godno večer!

2
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:12,000
 želim s vama podijeliti svoje razmišljanja o životnim pozivima.

3
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:21,000
 Zamolit ću Duha Svetoga da nam povede i da nam svoju riječ kako god on to želi.

4
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:31,000
 I am going to read to you from Romans 3:21

5
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:37,000
 Faith, the way to salvation.

6
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:46,000
 Yet, now we are told how God makes us just as he wants us to be without the law.

7
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:53,000
 This was already foretold in the law and the prophets.

8
00:00:54,000 --> 00:00:59,000
 God makes us righteous by means of faith in Jesus Christ.

9
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:07,000
 And this is applied to all who believe without distinction of persons.

10
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:13,000
 Because all have sinned and all fall short of the glory of God.

11
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:24,000
 and all are graciously forgiven and made holy through the redemption effected in Christ Jesus.

12
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:25,000
 So, I will read to you from the book of Romans 3:21.

