00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:21,000
 And what will be the case of a person that has a marriage vocation?

414
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:27,000
 It will be, Lord, here I am.

415
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:31,000
 I'm dying to get married.

416
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:37,000
 Please send me my husband or wife.

417
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:42,000
 Please do it soon.

418
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:45,000
 But let your will always be done.

419
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:50,000
 Obviously, that part always sounds weaker.

420
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:51,000
 Right?

421
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:57,000
 You will always say:

422
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:59,000
 Send me my husband soon.

423
00:11:59,000 --> 00:12:04,000
 And then very little say:

424
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:06,000
 Let your will be done.

425
00:12:10,000 --> 00:12:14,000
 But that is the way to do it.

426
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:17,000
 Because then you leave it up to God.

427
00:12:17,000 --> 00:12:21,000
